      "options": {
        "content": "### \u2139\ufe0f About This Report\nItem-level spend from FIS STDFSID XTRACT v1.3. **Click any tile** to jump to transaction or item detail.\n\n| Column | Source | Meaning |\n|---|---|---|\n| UPC | `fact_spend_item_detail.upc` | Product barcode |\n| Item Description | `fact_spend_item_detail.item_description` | Product name |\n| Spend Category | `fact_spend_item_detail.spend_category_code` | 5D=Food \u00b7 5A=OTC \u00b7 OF/OV=OTC variants |\n| Item Amount | `fact_spend_item_detail.item_amount` | Line item dollar amount |\n| Item Quantity | `fact_spend_item_detail.item_quantity` | Units purchased |\n| Settle Amount | `fact_spend_item.settle_amount` | Total transaction amount |\n\n> **393 items** \u00b7 **99 transactions** \u00b7 $4,824 total spend.",
